title: x/mobile: "unknown export data version: v1" on tip
body:
1. What version of Go are you using (`go version`)?
tip

2. What operating system and processor architecture are you using (`go env`)?
darwin/amd64

3. What did you do?
`gomobile bind` fails with error `unknown export data version: v1`
